- Image acquisition: Leica TCS SP5 and SP8; Olympus BX51WI;  Keyence BZ-X710 fluorescence microscope
- Electrophysiology: MultiClamp 700B and Digidata 1320A (Axon Instruments, Molecular Devices); P-97 Flaming/Brown Micropipette Puller (Sutter Instrument); ISO-Flex stimulus isolator;
- Single cell RNAseq: SMART-Seq v4 Kit (Takara Bio USA, Inc); 
